snippet.textDisplay:
Okay hear me out!
Isn’t the point of gourmet makes to find non-manufactured ways to make well loved foods? Not to torture Claire with time deadlines and high standards on recipes that no one is going to use??
Episodes like Oreos and snowball that have a good amount of challenge but are still fun for her are so much preferable. Thank you for coming to my ted talk.
